+// ============================================================================
+// Batch Operations (SIMD-friendly)
+// ============================================================================
+
+/// Batch multiply Q15 values.
+///
+/// Processes arrays of Q15 values efficiently. When SIMD is available,
+/// this can achieve 16× speedup using PMULHUW-style operations.
+///
